title: Grateful Dead Live at Orpheum Theater on 1976-07-18
lineage: technics rs-1506 reel>tascam hd-p2 compact flash 24/96>pc>adobe audition 2.0>cd wave>flac
description:
Set 1: 	 Mississippi Half-Step Uptown Toodeloo ; Cassidy ; Row Jimmy ; Mama Tried ; Scarlet Begonias ; Looks Like Rain ; Tennessee Jed ; New Minglewood Blues ; Loser ; The Music Never Stopped 

Set 2: 	Might As Well ; Samson And Delilah ; Candyman ; Lazy Lightnin' > Supplication > Let It Grow > Drums > Let It Grow > Jam > Wharf Rat > Space Jam > Drums > The Other One > Saint Stephen > Not Fade Away > Saint Stephen > The Wheel > The Other One (4) > Stella Blue ; Sugar Magnolia

Encore: Johnny B. Goode

reviews.review_text:
Thanks! I came across these reels in my quest to find the 10-6-77 Tempe broadcast

Thanks to Rob for transferring the 1/2 track reels for me

Brilliant Dead!! I had the FM version of this that I wore out! My all-time favorite Let it Grow to boot! Stellar versions of everything !
Saw a play in 2014 in the Orpheum; absolutely beautifully ornate gem of a venue in SF. Can't imagine seeing this go down while dosed!! Super special
